OL,6,F"SIA can confirm that we have sent out
OL,7,Fthe offers of compensation to the
OL,8,Fpassengers on 10 June 2024," by the
OL,9,Fcompany said.
OL,11,FGeoffrey Ralph Kitchen, a , died in
OL,12,Fthe incident, while
OL,14,FPassengers who sustained "minor
OL,15,Finjuries from the incident" have been
OL,16,Foffered $10,000 (#7,800), while those
OL,17,Fwho sustained "more serious injuries"
OL,18,Fhave been invited "to discuss a
OL,19,Fcompensation offer to meet each of
OL,20,Ftheir specific circumstances when they
OL,21,Ffeel well and ready to do so".
