OL,4,Cto turbulence victims
OL,6,FAs of June 4, 20 passengers injured in
OL,7,Fthe incident were still receiving
OL,8,Ftreatment in hospitals in Bangkok.
OL,10,F"Passengers medically assessed as
OL,11,Fhaving sustained serious injuries,
OL,12,Frequiring long-term medical care, and
OL,13,Frequesting financial assistance are
OL,14,Foffered an advance payment of
OL,15,FUS$25,000 (#19,600) to address their
OL,16,Fimmediate needs. This will be part of
OL,17,Fthe final compensation that these
OL,18,Fpassengers will receive."
