OL,3,CSingapore Airlines offers compensation
OL,4,Cto turbulence victims
OL,6,FFlight SQ321 was travelling to
OL,7,FSingapore from London Heathrow when it
OL,8,Fbegan to experience slight turbulence
OL,9,Fas it flew over a stormy area above
OL,10,FMyanmar at 8:49am UK time on 21 May, a
OL,11,Freport by The Transport Safety
OL,12,FInvestigation Bureau of Singapore said
OL,13,Flast month.
OL,15,FAs this slight turbulence set in about
OL,16,F10 hours after departure, the plane
OL,17,Fexperienced a rise in altitude by
OL,18,Faround 110 metres. At this point, the
OL,19,Fpilot announced the fasten seatbelt
OL,20,Fsign had been turned on.
