OL,6,FJust eight seconds later, a rapid
OL,7,Fchange in gravitational force caused
OL,8,Fan altitude drop of around 54 metres.
OL,10,FThe pilots disengaged autopilot,
OL,11,Fstabilised the aircraft and then re-
OL,12,Fengaged the autopilot. The plane then
OL,13,Fdiverted to Thailand, where passengers
OL,14,Freceived medical treatment.
